类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E> (implements java.util.Collection<E>)
      • java.util.AbstractList<E> (implements java.util.List<E>)
        • java.util.ArrayList<E> (implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.List<E>, java.util.RandomAccess, java.io.Serializable)
          • com.github.mybatis.pagination.Page<T>
    • org.springframework.jdbc.datasource.AbstractDataSource (implements javax.sql.DataSource)
      • com.github.mybatis.spring.DynamicDataSource (implements org.springframework.beans.factory.DisposableBean, org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean)
    • com.github.mybatis.interceptor.BaseInterceptor
      • com.github.mybatis.interceptor.PaginationAutoMapInterceptor (implements org.apache.ibatis.plugin.Interceptor)
    • org.springframework.context.annotation.ClassPathScanningCandidateComponentProvider (implements org.springframework.core.env.EnvironmentCapable, org.springframework.context.ResourceLoaderAware)
      • org.springframework.context.annotation.ClassPathBeanDefinitionScanner
        • com.github.mybatis.spring.ClassPathMapperScanner
    • com.github.mybatis.util.CloseableUtil
    • com.github.mybatis.provider.CrudProvider
    • org.springframework.dao.support.DaoSupport (implements org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean)
      • org.mybatis.spring.support.SqlSessionDaoSupport
        • com.github.mybatis.spring.MapperFactoryBean<T> (implements org.springframework.beans.factory.FactoryBean<T>)
    • com.github.mybatis.datatables.DataColumn (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • com.github.mybatis.datatables.DataRequest (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • com.github.mybatis.datatables.DataResponse<T> (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • com.github.mybatis.datatables.compatible.DataTablesRequest (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • com.github.mybatis.datatables.compatible.DataTablesResponse<T> (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • com.github.mybatis.util.EntityUtil
    • com.github.mybatis.entity.IdEntity (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • com.github.mybatis.spring.LazyConnection (implements java.lang.reflect.InvocationHandler)
    • com.github.mybatis.interceptor.MasterSlaveInterceptor (implements org.apache.ibatis.plugin.Interceptor)
    • com.github.mybatis.datatables.OrderColumn (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • com.github.mybatis.util.PersistMeta
    • com.github.mybatis.util.PropertiesLoader
    • com.github.mybatis.util.ReflectionUtil
    • com.github.mybatis.spring.ScannerConfigurer (implements org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware, org.springframework.beans.factory.support.BeanDefinitionRegistryPostProcessor, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanNameAware, org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean)
    • com.github.mybatis.datatables.SearchColumn (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • com.github.mybatis.handler.StringTypeUtf8mb4Handler (implements org.apache.ibatis.type.TypeHandler<T>)
    • com.github.mybatis.util.UnicodeFormatter

接口分层结构

  • com.github.mybatis.mapper.ICrudMapper<T>
    • com.github.mybatis.mapper.ICrudPaginationMapper<T> (并 extends com.github.mybatis.mapper.IPaginationMapper<T>)

  • com.github.mybatis.mapper.IPaginationMapper<T>
    • com.github.mybatis.mapper.ICrudPaginationMapper<T> (并 extends com.github.mybatis.mapper.ICrudMapper<T>)
